## API Endpoints

### tRPC Procedures (Implemented)
- `post.getPosts` - Retrieve all posts with ordering by creation date
- `post.createPost` - Create a new post with content validation (input: { content: string })
- `post.getPost` - Retrieve a single post by ID (input: { id: number })

### REST Endpoints
- `GET /health` - Health check endpoint
- `GET /` - Basic hello world endpoint
- `POST /trpc/*` - tRPC endpoint for all procedures

### Frontend API Routes
- `POST /api/trpc-proxy/[...trpc]` - Proxy route to backend tRPC server
- `GET /api/trpc-proxy/[...trpc]` - Proxy route for tRPC queries
- `OPTIONS /api/trpc-proxy/[...trpc]` - CORS preflight handling

